HEADWORD: Monovalent
<hw>Mo*nov"a*lent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Mono-</ets> + L. <ets>valens</ets>, p. pr. See
<er>Valence</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Having a valence of
